Short:        Sumeria is classic economic game
Author:       Eugene aGGreSSor Sobolev
Uploader:     amitrans()narod.ru (aGGreSSor/CPU)
Type:         game/text
Version:      19.3
Requires:     keyboard
Architecture: generic; m68k-amigaos; ppc-amigaos; i386-aros
Distribution: NonProfit

ooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooo
x                                                                             x
x  DESCRIPTION                                                                x
x                                                                             x
x     You, Hammurabi, the King of Babylonia, rule over your country making    x
x       the only decision worth making: where does this year's grain go?      x
x      For the food feeds the people now, buys land, or goes to planting      x
x                  for a very variable harvest for next year.                 x
x                                                                             x
x        Choose wisely and your country prospers: people immigrate from       x
x      foreign lands, you expand your land-holding,and the grain reserves     x
x                                 overflow.                                   x
x                                                                             x
x       Choose poorly, however, and you face the consequences of famine,      x
x                              plague, and poverty.                           x
x                                                                             x
ooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooo
x                                                                             x
x  CHANGELOG                                                                  x
x                                                                             x
x  Oct 2020:    rev.19.3                                                      x
x               - Results rounding added                                      x
x               - Internal context library update                             x
x               - "Try again?" has been moved to application                  x
x               - If you survived the rest doesn't matter                     x
x               - locale.library req.ver. for AmigaOS 3 reduced to V44        x
x               - Verified with AmigaOS 4.1 FE, AROS One 1.3 and AmiKit 8.5.3 x
x                                                                             x
x  Aug 2020:    rev.19.2 (first release)                                      x
x               - Extended text                                               x
x               - Locale support                                              x
x               - Amiga-like cross-compile support                            x
x               - Game logic fixed                                            x
x               - Clear screen added                                          x
x               - Years of Hammurabi's reign added                            x
x               - Veified with AmigaOS 4.1 FE, AROS One 1.3 and Coffin/OS R56 x
x                                                                             x
