x  1978:        "Kingdoms" by unknown, based on "Kingdom"                     x
x  1978:        "Hamurabi" by Peter Turnbull, 8K Microsoft Basic version      x
x  1975:        "Sumeria" by Mike Arnautov, BASIC heavily modified version    x
x  1973:        "Hamurabi" by David H. Ahl (DEC), DEC BASIC extended version  x
x  1972:        "Kingdom" by unknown, very enhanced BASIC version,            x
