x  For users                                                                  x
x                                                                             x
x         Just click on Sumeria icon for launch the game on your Amiga        x
x              AmigaOS version should be detected automatically               x
x                                                                             x
x  This is a fun classic economic game. If you want to win it, be merciless.  x
x              Game is demonstrates the basic tenet of CAPITALISM:            x
x     There is a citizen - there is a problem, no citizens - no one to eat    x
x                                It was a hint =)                             x
x                                                                             x
